# Phase 3.2 Worker Module Migration Plan - Revised

This revised plan details the implementation strategy to migrate the Worker module to a Hexagonal / Clean Architecture design pattern, incorporating copy-first isolation boundaries. Under this approach, legacy controllers and routes remain completely untouched and active until all clean use cases, repositories, and indexing schemes are fully validated.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Verification Gateways (Geospatial & Population):**
> We will verify that Mongoose `Booking.populate('workerId')` and geospatial `2dsphere` index lookups are fully active before introducing proxy wrappers on legacy files.

---

