*   **Controller Wrapper:** [src/controllers/workerController.js](file:///c:/Users/bibha/Desktop/sahayog-sarthi/backend/src/controllers/workerController.js)
*   **Router Wrapper:** [src/routes/worker.js](file:///c:/Users/bibha/Desktop/sahayog-sarthi/backend/src/routes/worker.js)

### Clean Architecture Components (New Files)
*   `Worker domain entity`: `src/modules/worker/domain/entities/Worker.js`
